---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CanvasScrollAnimation from '../components/CanvasScrollAnimation.jsx';
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<Layout>
	<!-- Fixed Canvas Background -->
	<div class="fixed top-0 left-0 -z-0 w-screen h-screen">
		<CanvasScrollAnimation client:only="react" />
	</div>

	<!-- Main Overlay Content Layer -->
	<main class="relative z-10 w-full min-h-[500vh] text-white selection:bg-white selection:text-black">
		
		<!-- 1. Hero Section -->
		<section class="w-full flex flex-col items-start justify-center text-left px-6 md:px-16 pt-[20vh] pb-[10vh] relative z-20">
			<h1 class="font-['Bebas_Neue'] text-[15vw] md:text-[12vw] leading-none tracking-tighter uppercase m-0 p-0 break-words text-left">
				ABI KURIAN<br/>VARGHESE
			</h1>
			
			<p class="font-['Inter'] text-sm md:text-lg tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mt-8 border-l-2 border-white/30 pl-4 text-white/80">
				Full-Stack Engineer / VFX & Cinematography
			</p>
			
			<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-start gap-4 mt-12 md:mt-16">
				<a href="#smart-yatra" class="border border-white rounded-full px-6 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest bg-transparent hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-colors duration-300 font-['Inter']">Smart Yatra</a>
				<a href="#visual-arts" class="border border-white rounded-full px-6 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest bg-transparent hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-colors duration-300 font-['Inter']">Visual Arts</a>
				<a href="#canvas-meta" class="border border-white rounded-full px-6 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest bg-transparent hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-colors duration-300 font-['Inter']">The Canvas</a>
				<a href="#about" class="border border-white rounded-full px-6 py-2 text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest bg-transparent hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-colors duration-300 font-['Inter']">About / Connect</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- 3. Case Study 1: Backend Engineering (Left Aligned) -->
		<section id="smart-yatra" class="px-6 md:px-16 max-w-4xl mt-[40vh] md:mt-[60vh] mb-16 md:mb-32">
			<div class="bg-black/40 mix-blend-screen border-l-2 border-white/20 p-6 md:p-12 reveal">
				<h2 class="font-['Bebas_Neue'] text-4xl md:text-8xl leading-none tracking-tight uppercase mb-8">
					SMART YATRA /<br />FLUTTER & DART
				</h2>
				<div class="font-['Inter'] text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed space-y-6 font-light">
					<p>
						Campus transit was plagued by unpredictable traffic and easily lost physical passes. Students needed a reliable, live-tracking ecosystem, but pinging GPS coordinates every second created a massive database bottleneck.
					</p>
					<p>
						To bypass Firebase quota limitations and battery drain, I engineered a dynamic geolocation throttling algorithm in Dart. The Flutter application calculates bus speed and proximity to stops, dynamically adjusting the cloud sync frequency. Paired with an offline caching system, it guarantees a seamless, batch-synced data flow even in dead zones.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- 4. Case Study 2: Visual Storytelling (Right Aligned) -->
		<section id="visual-arts" class="px-6 md:px-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:justify-end my-16 md:my-32">
			<div class="max-w-4xl bg-black/40 mix-blend-screen border-r-2 border-white/20 p-6 md:p-12 text-right reveal">
				<h2 class="font-['Bebas_Neue'] text-4xl md:text-8xl leading-none tracking-tight uppercase mb-8">
					NARRATIVE DIRECTION /<br />VFX & EDITING
				</h2>
				<div class="font-['Inter'] text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed space-y-6 font-light">
					<p>
						Technology is only half the equation; visual storytelling dictates the user experience. My digital editing workflow is defined by high-contrast aesthetics, beat-synchronization, and rigorous audience retention strategies across social platforms.
					</p>
					<p>
						This narrative focus extends into 3D environments and live-action direction. From conceptualizing 'Whispers of Silence'—a character-driven animation modeled in Blender—to directing short films that explore complex social dynamics and emotional twists, I actively bridge the gap between technical execution and creative direction.
					</p>
					<video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full h-auto mt-8 border border-white/20 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 ease-in-out object-cover aspect-video">
						<source src="/video/cinematography-reel.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
					</video>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- 5. The Meta Section (Left Aligned) -->
		<section id="canvas-meta" class="px-6 md:px-16 max-w-4xl my-16 md:my-32">
			<div class="bg-black/40 mix-blend-screen border-l-2 border-white/20 p-6 md:p-12 reveal">
				<h2 class="font-['Bebas_Neue'] text-4xl md:text-8xl leading-none tracking-tight uppercase mb-8">
					BEHIND THE CANVAS /<br />THE WILD SUNFLOWER
				</h2>
				<div class="font-['Inter'] text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed space-y-6 font-light">
					<p>
						The cinematic sequence scrubbing in the background of this portfolio is not a stock video. It is a custom 3D environment modeled, textured, and lit entirely from scratch in Blender.
					</p>
					<p>
						Rendered as a high-resolution, 150-frame image sequence, the animation is explicitly mapped to your scroll wheel using an HTML5 canvas and pure mathematics. The aesthetic intent is highly deliberate: creating a striking juxtaposition between the organic, delicate geometry of a wild sunflower and the rigid, stark-white brutalist code that defines the rest of this page.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- 6. The About Section (Left Aligned) -->
		<section id="about" class="px-6 md:px-16 max-w-4xl mt-16 md:mt-32 mb-[20vh]">
			<div class="bg-black/40 mix-blend-screen border-l-2 border-white/20 p-6 md:p-12 reveal">
				<h2 class="font-['Bebas_Neue'] text-4xl md:text-8xl leading-none tracking-tight uppercase mb-8">
					THE ARCHITECT /<br/>CONNECT
				</h2>
				<div class="font-['Inter'] text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed space-y-6 font-light">
					<p>
						Currently engineering systems and directing visuals in Kerala, India. I am actively seeking roles and freelance opportunities where I can bridge the gap between heavy data architecture and high-end visual storytelling.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-8 mt-10 font-['Bebas_Neue'] text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-widest">
					<a href="https://www.instagram.com/abii.aep/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-gray-400 transition-colors">INSTAGRAM</a>
					<a href="https://github.com/abikurian" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-gray-400 transition-colors">GITHUB</a>
					<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/abi-kurian-varghese/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-gray-400 transition-colors">LINKEDIN</a>
					<a href="mailto:abikurianvarghese@gmail.com" class="hover:text-gray-400 transition-colors">EMAIL</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>

	<script>
		document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
			const reveals = document.querySelectorAll(".reveal");
			const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
				entries.forEach((entry) => {
					if (entry.isIntersecting) {
						entry.target.classList.add("active");
					}
				});
			}, { threshold: 0.15 });
			
			reveals.forEach((reveal) => observer.observe(reveal));
		});
	</script>
</Layout>

<style>
	html {
		scroll-behavior: smooth;
		background: black;
	}
	
	.reveal {
		opacity: 0;
		transform: translateY(40px);
		transition: all 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
	}
	
	.reveal.active {
		opacity: 1;
		transform: translateY(0);
	}
</style>
